videoSnippet.title: Can Vassily Ivanchuk Defend His World Rapid Champion Title?
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator 12/26/2017 â€“ The "King Salman World Blitz & Rapid Championships 2017" in Riyadh from Decemer 26th to 30th. The first five rounds of the rapid tournament take place on December 26th. A record $2 million prize fund has attracted most of the world's best players.

Vassily Ivanchuk vs Surya Shekhar Ganguly
King Salman World Rapid Championship, Riyadh, rd 2, Dec-26 
English Opening: King's English Variation (A20)

1. c4 e5 2. g3 Nf6 3. Bg2 d5 4. cxd5 Nxd5 5. Nf3 Nc6 6. O-O Nb6 7. d3 Be7 8. Nbd2 O-O 9. a3 a5 10. b3 Re8 11. Bb2 Bf8 12. Nc4 Nxc4 13. bxc4 Nd4 14. Nxe5 Rxe5 15. e3 c5 16. Re1 Bf5 17. exd4 Rxe1+ 18.
